1. Make twitter treads once a week at least of your learnings.
2. Don't use too many hashtags in your tweet. (one hashtag is enough)
3. If you are attending any Hackathon then Tweet about that hackathon and tag the Organisers.
4. If you have any doubts then try to ask in public or to solve the problems who asked in public.
5. Get involved in the Twitter space and try to interact with people there. 
6. Follow those people only from whom you are getting knowledge.
7. Don't post any offensive tweets
8. Get involved in global communities.
